CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 17, 1965, pg. 24, reads: "Gabfest - Diamond talk was the order of the day at Forbes Field, on Monday, prior to the beginning of the opening day game between the Pirates and the Giants. The left photo shows three players, who carry a lot of lumber, discussing batting tips.  The performers are, Donn Clendenon, Willie McCovey and Willie Stargell..."
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Pirates baseball player Donn Clendenon, San Francisco Giants Willie McCovey, and Pirates Willie Stargell, posed on Forbes Field for 1965 season opener
